identiconpp
------------------------------------------
identiconpp is a library to generate identicons for C++.

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-3.6.9-1
  libMagick-devel-7.1.2.11-1
  libMagickC++7_5-7.1.2.11-1
  libgcc1-13.4.0-1
  libidenticonpp0-0.7.3-1bl2
  libstdc++6-13.4.0-1
  pkg-config-2.5.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.46.1-1
  cmake-4.2.1-1
  cygport-0.37.7-1
  gcc-core-13.4.0-1
  gcc-g++-13.4.0-1
  libMagick-devel-7.1.2.11-1
  ninja-1.13.2-1

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/tastytea/identiconpp

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/tastytea/identiconpp/archive/refs/tags/0.7.3.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack identiconpp-0.7.3-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./identiconpp-0.7.3-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/identiconpp-0.7.3-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/identiconpp-0.7.3-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libidenticonpp0-0.7.3-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libidenticonpp-devel-0.7.3-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(identiconpp)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/identiconpp.README
  /usr/share/doc/identiconpp/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/identiconpp/README.adoc

(libidenticonpp0)
  /usr/bin/cygidenticonpp-0.dll

(libidenticonpp-devel)
  /usr/include/identiconpp.hpp
  /usr/lib/cmake/identiconpp/identiconppConfig.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/identiconpp/identiconppConfigVersion.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/identiconpp/identiconppTargets-release.cmake
  /usr/lib/cmake/identiconpp/identiconppTargets.cmake
  /usr/lib/libidenticonpp.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/identiconpp.pc

